title: Reserve Your 3BR Now! Brand New 55+ Apartment Home Rentals!
posting_body: ['Take a Video Tour Today', '> Check out the video walkthroughs of our community’s amenities and apartment homes!', 'If you are interested in an in-person tour, feel free to call or email us at any time.', 'Please use the link in this ad to view our video tours & options to contact us directly.', 'The Legends of Apple Valley, our independent 55+ apartment living community captures the essence of living well.', 'We offer a beautiful community room with a full kitchen and fireplace, beauty salon, and theatre room.', 'Our residents may also enjoy the 24-hour fitness center, craft and card room, and underground heated parking.', 'With our convenient location, there is no better place than The Legends of Apple Valley to call your new home!', 'Community Amenities Include:', '- Craft and card rooms', '- Theatre room', '- Professional management team', '- Heated underground parking', '- Large walk-in closets', 'We are a pet friendly community!', 'Dogs & cats welcome!', '*Comfortable living does not have to be high dollar.', 'The Legends of Apple Valley is a 55 or better senior community and participates in an affordable housing program.', 'Household income & student status limitations apply: 1 Occupant: $49,320 | 2', 'Occupants: $56,340 | 3', 'Occupants: $63,360 | 4 Occupants: $70,380.', 'To maintain the integrity of the community; credit, rental & public record background checks are conducted on all applicants.', 'Office Hours:', 'Monday-Friday:9:00AM-5:00PM', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'Legends of Apple Valley', '14050 Granite Ave.', 'Apple Valley, MN, 55124', '<URL>', '*Some Restrictions May Apply.', 'd71xtMC7']
